  "title": "Broken SSR when using InfiniteHitsSessionStorageCache",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\n\nSSR in Next.js is currently broken when used together with `createInfiniteHitsSessionStorageCache`.\n\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\n\n1. Load more results\r\n2. Hard refresh page\r\n3. Hydration error will be displayed\n\n### Live reproduction\n\nhttps://codesandbox.io/p/sandbox/white-rgb-t5lkyg\n\n### 💭 Expected behavior\n\nSkip loading cache on hydration.\n\n### Package version\n\nreact-instantsearch-hooks-web 6.47.1\n\n### Operating system\n\n_No response_\n\n### Browser\n\n_No response_\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
